cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs), in the field of computer vision and machine learning for Bangla License Plate Recognition. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper also discusses the use of state-of-the-art accuracy and benchmarks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The creation and release of a standard database for BLPRS could also indicate that the paper could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
